channel.description:
[size=30pt]I Will Post Pictures LATER!!!!!!!!!! as i am not feeling well right now x.x[/size] *first release* http://moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,336778.0.html Credits: Delta for the base :o 1xiix1 for full dueling Me ar-temi-s for stuff i added :p Knova for some commands and helping me change Dbow max :p
Hey there moparscape people!
I am release my server! :p
Features:*most of the stuff already in deltascape :P* [size=20pt]i did not add any of these![/size] Full dueling* credits go to 1xiix1 Pest control fight pits wildy levels full fight cave
Features i added in v1! added xp gain from Pest control added Npc's to pestcontrol that attack you! added npc on the pest control boat to tell you how much time till game starts added npc in fight pit waiting room to tell how much time till match starts
Features i added in v2! Changed all god sword's max hits! armadyl gs - 90 Bandos gs - 80 Saradomin gs - 70 Zamorak gs- 60 Made d bow's spec max hit 90!!! *45-45* Added a library! Added npc's in library that give xp You need a Library card to get in Library! * cost 10m* Adding never before used shopping zone! Added More Npc Dialogues Added A way to get to mining zone! Added New client items!
Pictures from v1! *still in source lol *
[IMG]http://i40.tinypic.com/m7yq95.png[/img]
[IMG]http://i39.tinypic.com/4uw6de.png[/img]
Now the download link!! Source http://www.mediafire.com/download.php?tqbzy2nm4yo Client http://www.mediafire.com/?sharekey=9e459b240bb53513391d7d881749d3a7e04e75f6e8ebb871
